casebody.data:
Jeremy HOOKER, Appellee,
v.
Brenda M. MOORE, Appellant. SC: 158983
COA: 343334 Supreme Court of Michigan. June 5, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the December 11, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the question presented should be reviewed by this Court.
